                                "props": { "content": "<p style='color:#1c1917;font-size:1.05rem'><strong>Filet de boeuf, sauce au poivre</strong> <span style='color:#d97706;float:right'>32 &euro;</span></p><p style='color:#78716c;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:16px'>Filet de boeuf Angus muri 30 jours, gratin dauphinois, legumes de saison.</p><p style='color:#1c1917;font-size:1.05rem'><strong>Risotto aux cepes et parmesan</strong> <span style='color:#d97706;float:right'>26 &euro;</span></p><p style='color:#78716c;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:16px'>Riz carnaroli, cepes frais, copeaux de parmesan 24 mois, huile de truffe.</p><p style='color:#1c1917;font-size:1.05rem'><strong>Dorade royale grillee</strong> <span style='color:#d97706;float:right'>28 &euro;</span></p><p style='color:#78716c;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:16px'>Filet de dorade, ecrasee de pommes de terre, beurre blanc aux herbes.</p><p style='color:#1c1917;font-size:1.05rem'><strong>Magret de canard au miel et epices</strong> <span style='color:#d97706;float:right'>29 &euro;</span></p><p style='color:#78716c;font-size:0.9rem'>Magret rose, jus au miel et quatre-epices, puree de patate douce.</p>" }
